*Izazov* je da se bude inovativan. (The challenge is to be innovative.)

Ne smemo da se plašimo *izazova*. (We must not be afraid of the challenges.)

Ona je preuzela *izazov* da to uradi. (She took on the challenge to do that.)

Taj *izazov* je ključan za uspeh. (This challenge is key to success.)

Njegov *izazov* je bio da prebrodi teškoće. (His challenge was to overcome difficulties.)